ActIndian Act
SubjectLong Plain Indian Reserve No. 6, Manitoba ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise by the MANITOBA HYDRO-ELECTRIC BOARD of the power to take an interest in lands within LONG PLAIN INDIAN RESERVE NO. 6, in Manitoba; and (2) granting the Company the required easement.
